With so many SuperSport channels available, sports fans find themselves wishing they could watch on multiple screens – especially when matches are scheduled for the same time. The DStv Now app solves this problem neatly, allowing users to stream two different SuperSport channels at the same time. In practice, this means: It doesn’t matter which configuration or devices are used; the DStv Now app makes it possible to watch DStv content on two devices simultaneously. On 12 and 13 March, DStv Now will be streaming two UEFA Champions League matches live and free! The following matches will be streamed: Fans don’t need to be DStv subscribers, they only need to be using DStv Now online or on their devices. This article was published in partnership with DStv Now.